      "title":            "What matters to you in a relationship?",
      "body":             "Terms of Us helps you put words on a relationship: what is already there, what you would like, what deserves a conversation, and what does not work for you.\n\nStart with the categories that speak to you. You do not need to fill in everything: the goal is to identify what truly matters to you.\n\nYou can then review your summary, read it back, and share it if you want to open a conversation.",
